What is controller containment and what does it offer developers?\
\pard\tx720\tx1440\tx2160\tx2880\tx3600\tx4320\tx5040\tx5760\tx6480\tx7200\tx7920\tx8640\pardirnatural\qr\partightenfactor0

\b0 \cf0 >> Controller containment is when one view controller places another view controller inside it. It is useful to developers because it keeps things organized and less messy. It allows them to break up the view controller into separate view controllers that each have their own logic and goals.
